        <section id="classroom">
            <h1>Zazu Classroom (Aftercare)</h1>
            <p>Our Zazu Aftercare program provides a safe, fun, and engaging environment for school-aged children after their school day. We offer a mix of structured activities and free play.</p>

            <h2>Program Agenda</h2>
            <p>The aftercare program is designed to be a relaxing and enriching extension of the school day. Activities include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Homework Help:</strong> Dedicated time and support for completing school assignments.</li>
                <li><strong>Creative Play:</strong> Access to art supplies, board games, and building blocks.</li>
                <li><strong>Outdoor Recreation:</strong> Time for sports and games to release energy.</li>
                <li><strong>Group Activities:</strong> Storytelling, team-building games, and special projects.</li>
                <li><strong>Social Interaction:</strong> Encouraging positive relationships among peers.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
